Name: UCSB
Description: A great university located along the California coast!

Name: IUPUI
Description: A bustling university where my boyfriend is a geography major!

Name: Muir Woods
Description: A beautiful monument of towering redwood trees in northern California. The air is crisp and I love to go here with family and friends!

Name: Mapparium
Description: In the Christian Church of Science in Boston, Massachussets is a beautiful three-story tall globe made out of stained glass that surrounds you. It is definitely a must see for anyone who loves geography.

Name: Parliament Hill
Description: This is Canada's parliament building located in Ottawa, the country's capital! My boyfriend and I had a lovely walk around here and even saw a lights show displayed on the historic building at night!

Name: Great Smoky Mountains
Description: A beautiful expanse of nature in Tennessee, not too far from Dollywood! I went here during wildflower season and got to experience some beautiful sights during my hikes!
